Refactoring Steps
-----
* p. 285-6: Adding Coffee and Tea. BoilWater() and PourInCup() are the exact same methods for both classes.
* p. 290-3: Abstracting PrepareRecipe(). Added CaffeineBeverage superclass.

Lessons
